{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"621","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"擺脫塑膠大國稱號 泰國推各式減塑政策","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/01/28 18:26</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;&#10;font-family:'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%A1%91%E8%86%A0.jpg' style='width: 700px; height: 933px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>泰國要擺脫塑膠大國的稱號，<span lang='EN-US'>75</span>家零售業者從元旦起不再提供顧客一次性塑膠袋，希望每年減少<span lang='EN-US'>30%</span>、也就是<span lang='EN-US'>135</span>億個塑膠袋使用量。中央社記者呂欣憓曼谷攝<span lang='EN-US'> 109</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>28</span>日</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>（中央社記者呂欣憓曼谷<span lang='EN-US'>28</span>日專電）泰國努力擺脫塑膠大國的名號，近幾年推出許多活動和政策提高泰國人環保意識，最新措施是商店和超市不提供一次性塑膠袋，已於今年元旦上路，成效如何仍有待觀察。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>東南亞國家製造的塑膠垃圾量在全球名列前茅，根據泰國匯商銀行經濟與商業研究中心研究，泰國是全世界第<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>大海洋塑膠垃圾製造國，僅次於中國、印尼、菲律賓、越南和斯里蘭卡。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>泰國是大量使用塑膠製品的國家，根據聯合國資料，<span lang='EN-US'>2016</span>年在泰國沿海省分收集到<span lang='EN-US'>1078</span>萬噸的垃圾，其中<span lang='EN-US'>130</span>萬噸是塑膠垃圾。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>以曼谷市為例，曼谷市政府每天收到的垃圾有多達<span lang='EN-US'>8000</span>萬個塑膠袋，市民約為<span lang='EN-US'>1000</span>多萬人，平均每人每天使用多達<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>個塑膠袋。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>泰國想要展現減塑決心，<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>6</span>月在泰國舉行的東南亞國家協會高峰會就通過了「曼谷宣言」（<span lang='EN-US'>Bangkok Declaration on Combating Marine Debris in ASEAN Region</span>），指出各國認知到海洋垃圾多數來自陸地，誓言要與各國共同合作，減少海洋垃圾。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>根據泰國汙染控制局（<span lang='EN-US'>Pollution Control Department</span>）統計，泰國每年用掉<span lang='EN-US'>450</span>億個塑膠袋，其中<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>成約<span lang='EN-US'>180</span>億個塑膠袋來自傳統市場或是街頭小販，其中<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>成約<span lang='EN-US'>135</span>億個來自零售業者，還有<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>成來自超市和百貨公司。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>泰國零售業協會（<span lang='EN-US'>Thai Retailers Association</span>）因此發起了減塑活動，<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年起每個月第<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>天為無塑膠袋日，當時有<span lang='EN-US'>42</span>家企業加入，零售業協會並從<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>4</span>日到<span lang='EN-US'>2019</span>年的<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>月<span lang='EN-US'>31</span>日發起點數回饋活動，過去兩年因此減少了<span lang='EN-US'>20</span>億個塑膠袋使用量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>為了減少更多塑膠袋使用量，零售業協會更決定發起每天向塑膠袋說不活動，加入協會的<span lang='EN-US'>75</span>家企業共<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>萬<span lang='EN-US'>4500</span>個通路，從今年元旦起，全面停止提供免費塑膠袋，希望每年減少<span lang='EN-US'>30%</span>、也就是<span lang='EN-US'>135</span>億個塑膠袋使用量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>泰國政府更打算從明年開始禁止商家使用塑膠杯和塑膠吸管。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>這並非泰國第一次推出大型減塑活動，泰國政府在<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>月開始，在全國<span lang='EN-US'>154</span>座國家公園禁止塑膠袋、吸管、保麗龍和塑膠杯碗盤等一次性塑膠製品進入園區；<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年不少連鎖的旅館業者宣布不提供一次性塑膠沐浴用品、吸管和瓶裝水。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>泰國國家海洋與沿海資源部（<span lang='EN-US'>Department of Marine and Coastal Resources</span>）還訂出<span lang='EN-US'>2027</span>年減塑目標，希望屆時每個泰國人每天使用的塑膠袋減少至<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>個，同時訂定短、中、長期減塑計畫，希望將海中和海岸垃圾減少一半。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>但消費者習慣並非一夕可以改變，民族報（<span lang='EN-US'>The Nation</span>）在去年<span lang='EN-US'>9</span>月曾經實地走訪各大商店和超市，發現多數消費者仍然習慣買東西要塑膠袋，這次元旦起業者不提供塑膠袋，是否可以扭轉多數人的使用習性，仍待進一步觀察。（編輯：林憬屏<span lang='EN-US'>1090128</span>）</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202001280162.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-31","clk_count":"107"}},"__N_SSG":true}